      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know i should talk to the doc but i literally have an appointment in like 3 weeks. i just feel like i'm overmedicated right now. if i start taking 2mg now instead of 5mg, is it really going to be that different? it's a pretty small jump, surely my blood can handle a slightly lower dose for a couple of weeks until i see them?",
